Sports Shooting USA (c) 2003 Sammy.

Compete on the speed, accuracy, and technique in this faithful reproduction of the world of target shooting. Guns are the exclusive Sammy scope gun with laser sight. Single or twin player game, which allows you to play against the computer or a friend. The game is very addictive giving you the chance to improve your ability to score the highest points, qualifying you to the next level. After the end of the events you are then graded. There are four levels from Beginner to Master, and you can play up to a hundred different events. The targets vary between moving targets and still targets, so keep your eyes peeled!

